cdata.name: CashBagCoin
cdata.desc:
CashBagis a blockchain-based platform for instant settlement and micropayments of cash back rewards. The platform will use the Ethereum blockchain to provide an instant settlement platformwith low transactions costs and a reward system that helps shoppers to earn cash back and secure discounts on any online purchase.

CashBagCoin is an ERC-20 compliant token, that will serve as the utility token on the platform.
